    <p>Edmond Phiri is a transformational coach helping resilient individuals rise from survival to significance. With deep roots in lived experience and professional growth, he guides others to find identity, lead with peace, and serve with power.</p>
  </section>

  <section id="rise" class="section">
    <h2>The RISE Process™</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>R:</strong> Reflect – uncover your true story</li>
      <li><strong>I:</strong> Identify – break limiting beliefs and roles</li>
      <li><strong>S:</strong> Strengthen – rebuild with clarity and purpose</li>
      <li><strong>E:</strong> Execute – lead yourself and others boldly</li>
    </ul>
